p: The results of the GC-MS analysis on a Î²-cyclodextrin enantioselective column are reported in Table 2, including both the enantiomeric distribution and the enantiomeric excess ( ee) for each enantiomeric couple. The chromatogram of the enantioselective analysis is shown in Figure 2; only the enantiomeric couples that underwent separation have been reported. It is worthy of note that most of the detected enantiomers were baseline separated.
